  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She came with me to San Francisco, and she lived here with us in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in retrospect, I'm not sure I did the right thing, because while we gave her as loving an environment as was humanly possible, she was at an age where, perhaps, she should have stayed with her friends and in a place with familiar language and customs and food and what not.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was in Los Angeles on university business when I heard that-- that she had a heart attack and passed away here in-- in San Francisco.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those three boys who died in labor camp were--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two of them were her children, and one of them was the child of the other sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's no date, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is no date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a gradual awareness that-- that-- you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was no-- no sign of any kind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- I-- I must admit that I-- I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was not surprised.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not surprised.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I-- I threw myself into reading about this period as soon as the war was over, and articles and books were beginning to appear.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and that process hasn't stopped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't think I understand it any better now than I did in 1945 of what happened, because there is no rational way of explaining it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm a very rational person.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And while the enormity of the literature add to our understanding of the details and the nuances, if you had-- if you read 50 Holocaust memoirs, you could have read 500 Holocaust memoirs.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as this project, it-- it-- it fills in bits of the mosaic, but it really doesn't explain anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
